---
layout: base
title: Spectacles
description: Programmation et prochains spectacles de la troupe de théatre d'improvisation le Poulailler de l'Impro
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Programmation
  order: 1

eleventyImport:
  collections: ["spectacle"]
---

<h1>{{ title }}</h1>

<section>
    <h2>À venir</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {% for spectacle in collections.spectacle | upcoming(collections.spectacle) %}
            <div class="max-w-sm bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                <a href={{spectacle.url}}>
                    <img class="rounded-t-lg" src={{spectacle.data.poster}} alt=""/>
                </a>
                <div class="p-5">
                    <a href="#">
                        <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                            {{spectacle.data.title}}
                        </h5>
                    </a>
                    <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">
                        {{spectacle.data.description}}
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Au {{ spectacle.data.place }} le {{ spectacle.data.date.toLocaleDateString("fr") }} à {{spectacle.data.time}}</p>
                    <a href={{spectacle.url}} class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white bg-blue-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 hover:text-white focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:text-white dark:focus:ring-blue-800"> En savoir plus
                        <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 -mr-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Passés</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            {% for spectacle in collections.spectacle | past(collections.spectacle) %}
                <div class="max-w-sm bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <div class="p-5">
                        <a href="{{ spectacle.url }}">
                            <p>{{ spectacle.data.title }}</p>
                            <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">
                                Au {{ spectacle.data.place }} le {{ spectacle.data.date.toLocaleDateString("fr") }} à {{spectacle.data.time}}</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>